## 🛠️ Troubleshooting Quick Reference

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| "Network Error" on OTP | Check LAN IP in [api.js](file:///d:/ASTURA/svakarma-mobile/myapp/services/api.js) line 18 matches `ipconfig` IPv4 |
| "No token provided" on Submit | Log out and log back in (OTP flow must complete) |
| App stuck loading at 0% | Wi-Fi isolation — try PC hotspot instead |
| Backend error on startup | Check `backend/.env` has `PORT=5000` and `JWT_SECRET` set |
| Score not fetching | Make sure you are logged in (JWT stored) before visiting CIBIL screen |
